Dependencies (Ubuntu Package Names):

- gcc-4.5
- libtbb-dev
- libboost-dev >= 1.45
- boost numeric bindings http://mathema.tician.de/software/boost-numeric-bindings
- xsdcxx                 for config file XML parsing
- python-scipy
- mayavi2                for visualization
- ipython                for mayavi and parallelization

go to dijkstra directory and run 

$ make

this builds the C++ part of the project.
